430
00:19:09,115 --> 00:19:10,275
Of course, baby.

431
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,950
I love you.

432
00:19:12,018 --> 00:19:14,348
I love you, too.

433
00:19:14,421 --> 00:19:16,461
See? Right there,
how did you
just do that?

434
00:19:16,523 --> 00:19:18,533
How'd you just
fix everything?
I don't know.

435
00:19:18,591 --> 00:19:22,061
I guess sometimes
you just have to
set your ego aside.

436
00:19:22,128 --> 00:19:26,368
Yeah. And remember that
the love that you have
for that other person

437
00:19:26,433 --> 00:19:29,343
is way more important
than winning.

438
00:19:31,971 --> 00:19:33,441
(BOTH LAUGHING)

439
00:19:33,506 --> 00:19:35,166
More important
than winning.

440
00:19:35,242 --> 00:19:36,912
Stop, stop it.

441
00:19:36,976 --> 00:19:39,676
