442
00:19:39,746 --> 00:19:42,476
Okay, look,
the honeymoon period
may be over,

443
00:19:42,549 --> 00:19:46,119
but now you can get
into the real stuff.

444
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:49,685
And honestly,
that's the best part.

445
00:19:49,756 --> 00:19:51,856
Good night.

446
00:19:51,924 --> 00:19:53,694
